text
@Plan to scrape metacritic:
URL:
http://www.metacritic.com/game/pc/goat-simulator

Title:
<span itemprop="name">
    Goat Simulator
</span>

Description for game looks like this:
<ul class="summary_details">
    <li class="summary_detail product_summary">
        <span class="label">Summary:</span>
        <span class="data" itemprop="description">
            <span>
                Goat Simulator is the latest in goat simulation technology, 
                bringing next-gen goat simulation to YOU. You no longer have to 
                fantasize about being a goat, your dreams have finally been 
                realized!
            </span>
        </span>
    </li>
</ul>

Boxart looks like this:
<div class="product_image large_image">
    <img class="product_image large_image"
         alt="Goat Simulator Image" 
         src="http://static.metacritic.com/images/products/games/9/55ee9f422ffc9d846f81ee758df545d3-98.jpg" 
         itemprop="image">
</div>

Rating looks like this:
<div class="metascore_w xlarge game mixed">
    <meta content="100" itemprop="bestRating">
    <span itemprop="ratingValue">62</span>
</div>

Review stats look like this:
<div class="review_stats">
    <div class="review_critic">
        <div class="source">
            <a href="/publication/gameplanet?filter=games">Gameplanet</a>
        </div>
        <div class="date">
            Apr  1, 2014
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review_grade">
        <div class="metascore_w medium game positive indiv">
            90
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

Review Summary looks like this:
<div class="review_body">
    Goat Simulator is the worst best game you have to play at all costs. It is
    unique, and definitely will grow thanks to its already active community.
</div>

How Long To Beat Table looks like this:
<div class="gprofile_times backdarkish">
    <li>
        <h5>Main Story</h5>
        <div class="time_40">2 Hours</div>
    </li>
    <li>
        <h5>Main+Extras</h5>
        <div class="time_40">3 Hours</div>
    </li>
    <li>
        <h5>Completionist</h5>
        <div class="time_50">5 Hours</div>
    </li>
    <li>
        <h5>Combined</h5>
        <div class="time_50">4 Hours</div>
    </li>
</div>

How Long to Beat Picture looks like this:
<div class="gprofile_image backlight shadow_box">
    <img style="width: 100%;" src="gameimages/Goat_Simulator.jpg">
</div>
